text: eheyin daham dutavarun aturin dædi adhisthanayen vuvan ivasuvak men numba da ivasanu. tavada ovun sandaha numba ikman novanu. ovunata pratigna denu læbu dæ ovun dakina dina dahaval kalaye horavak misa taman natara novuvak meni. (numbe karyaya) dænum dimaki. papatara janaya hæra (venat kisiveku) vinasa karanu labanneda
